{"type": "article", "id": 28859, "title": "落地灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-29T06:59:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121801GEFPSk0UIALgaDB9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>乌克兰设计师 <a href=\"http://levantindesign.com/\">Sergey Levantin</a> 的作品大多由纤细的几何线条构成。FITMENTS 是他最新设计的一款落地灯，灯泡和电线直接被金属框架所包围，看起来既简洁又大方。由于摒弃了传统的灯罩和灯柱，FITMENTS 带给人一种轻盈的感觉，适合放在空间较小的环境当中。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121759pogbaKIcekMmtr7R.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121759do8i1nhQeDGt4azU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121800Y9815HzZsdbaxpWE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121800Ou3CyTxVYjkLZ2Xt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}